def: A dance or game played by boys, requiring active exercise.[Obs.] Gayton.
A flowing round on all sides; an inclosing with a fluid.

Of, pertaining to, or designating, an acid, C8H12O4 (calledalso terpentic acid), homologous with terebic acid, and obtained as awhite crystalline substance by the oxidation of oil of turpentinewith chromic acid.
A plant of Sierra Leone which yields a wholesome, creamy juice.
To ret or rot by the process called dewretting.
Having the properties of a nonmetal; nonmetallic; acid;negative.
Turning or facing inward, or toward the axis of the part towhich it belongs. Gray.
